Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need your oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新矿石的第一丝踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first traces of a new ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德保证 吉尔加拉德派他来这里并没有恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond has been very convincing in his assurances
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德的话让人非常信服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Gil-galad bore no ill intent when he sent him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉事有蹊跷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is something more at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去林顿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Lindon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find out what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被踢出海上卫队了  你们仨全部淘汰 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're off the Sea Guard! All three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毁了朋友们的生活 羞辱了家门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just ruined my friends' lives, shamed our family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找那些在旧瞭望塔避难的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to the Men who have taken refuge in the old watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们捎个口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deliver to them a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人民要想保全性命 必须放弃这些土地的所有权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That your people may live if you forsake all claim to these lands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并向他宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and swear fealty to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我们真正的国王会归来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One day, our true king will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你关在地牢里的那一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe the man you hold in your dungeons 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是流亡在外 下落不明的南方大地王位继承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the lost heir in exile to the throne of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请求您与我并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I call on you to fight with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我愿意出征  -我愿意出征 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I will serve! -I will serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免索隆将他们的土地据为己有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...before Sauron claims their lands for his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have lied, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把危险的外族人带了进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}brought a dangerous outsider into our midst.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要掉队了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们大家不会掉队的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is how we keep up with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他会帮我们 我们也会帮他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He helps us, and... and we help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指环王：力量之戒\N第一季第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“千禧”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My great thumb. My great thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 应该念迁…迁徙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Mi... Migration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迁-徙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, mi-gra-tion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是搬家 我们毛脚族搬家就叫做迁徙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Means, like, to move. What we do, Harfoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 我们会去老林子过冬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, we... we winter in Old Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲夏时节 我们会 趁蜗牛鲜美时前往诺菲德山谷捕食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and mid-summer, we make for Norfield Glen to snail while the snailing's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-“蜗牛”  -没错 蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-"Snails, snails"? -Snails, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在橡树叶刚刚开始变红的秋天 我们前往格罗夫果园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And at the first blush of the oak leaves, we head to the Grove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个果园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A whole orchard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是苹果 李子 杏子 胡萝卜 你肯定很喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}popping with bar apples, plums, apricots, carrots, you'll... you'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 唯一的麻烦是 从一地迁徙到另一地要历经重重危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, the only trouble is there's a hundred perils between here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“危险” \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Perils"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like a danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如人类 狼群 雾 雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, big folk, wolves, fog, rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山岭食人妖 洞穴食人妖 只要能杀死你的都算是威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hill-trolls, cave-trolls, anything that'll kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“杀死” \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Kill"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是把某个东西弄死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Means to make somethin' dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是个危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, no, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-更像是说… -不 萤火虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It's more... -No. Fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次意外 就是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-That was just an accident. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not a peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很好 因为你是来帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're good. Because you're here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 其他人现在应该准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, great. Others should be ready by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小腿跑起来 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quick sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再敢用那根拐杖戳我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poke me with that crutch again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就趁你睡觉的时候 拔掉你脚趾上的毛发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll pluck the hair off your toes in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你拔毛的时候 顺便把我的耳朵也揪掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll pluck off my ears while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省得我再听你的鼾声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'd save me listenin' to your snorin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴吧 我才不打呼噜呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, stuff. I do not snore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你确实打呼噜 -你确实打呼噜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 动起来 不迈腿永远都去不了格罗夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, now. Grove's not gonna migrate to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是给我们唱你妈妈的赶路歌 没准能帮我们走快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might help us move faster if you sang us your mam's walking song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 唱吧 波比 喊两嗓子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, go on, Pops, give us a warble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧 能给我们赶路加油鼓劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on, it'll do us some good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳正在落下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The sun is fast fallin'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落在森岩的树林后方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beneath trees of stone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔中之光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The light in the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No longer my home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去灯火朦胧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Past eyes of pale fire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沙做我的睡床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Black sand for my bed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用所知的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I trade all I've known
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换取未知的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the unknown ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤我 遥远之地 请呼唤我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call to me Call to me lands far away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗瓦尼安之丘-韦德布鲁克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我现在 必须在这流浪的日子里游荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For I must now wander this wandering day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副崖-灰色沼泽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须游荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Away I must wander
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这流浪的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wandering day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我缺水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of drink I have little
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我少食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And food I have less
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量告诉我不行 但是这条路要求我踏足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My strength tells me no But the path demands yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲑鳟弯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我双腿很短 而道阻且长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My legs are so short And the way is so long
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法休息 何谈舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've no rest nor comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所慰藉 唯有歌声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No comfort, but song
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西斯尔戴尔-辫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我歌唱 遥远之地 请为我歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sing to me, sing to me Lands far away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请起身指引我度过这流浪的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, rise up and guide me This wandering day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请答应要找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please promise to find me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个流浪的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-This wandering day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 他们的答案来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-At last comes their answer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过寒冷和霜冻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Through cold and through frost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有的流浪者都身陷迷途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That not all who wonder or wander are lost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter the sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不计成本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter the cost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有的流浪者都身陷迷途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That not all who wonder Or wander are... Lost
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隧道挖通了 大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tunnel is complete, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看你的手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your arm. Show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像被火烤一样疼 父亲大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like fire, Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望你能像我一样感受阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you could feel it like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太阳很快就要消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For soon, it will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身体里能感受到温暖的那部分 也将随之消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with it, the part of me that knew its warmth as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想念它的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shall miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了 去召集军团吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Summon the legions. It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人扬言要发起进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Our enemy vows to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想活命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In exchange for mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人命令我们放弃这座瞭望塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've been ordered to abandon this tower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并向他们的指挥官宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and swear fealty to their commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我不是 你们翘首以盼的那个国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know I'm not the king you have awaited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你们选择和我并肩战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you choose to stand with me and fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这座瞭望塔 将不再会是我们脆弱的招牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this tower will no longer be a reminder of our frailty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而将会变成我们力量的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but a symbol of our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁愿意和我并肩作战 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who will stand with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当中有谁愿意奋起作战 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who among you will stand and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 我们战斗吧 -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Aye, let's do it. -Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋起作战 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋起作战 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说 我们最好碰碰运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say it'd be better to take our chances
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣服于所谓的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bowing to the supposed enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直视过敌人的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have looked that enemy in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拯救不了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not your deliverance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你觉得你能 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指望精灵 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要替祖先说句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll say this for our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人并没有杀他们啊 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要团结一致 我们就能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together, we can survive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟我走 我们必定会活下来 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow me, and together, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 都跟我走 来吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Let's go. Come on. Follow me. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奥 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的好机会 好时机 快来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's our chance. It's our time. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起走 来吧 小伙子 跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With me. Come on, lad. Follow me, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我一把吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Okay. Give me a hand, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再高点…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Higher. Higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子们 这一轮足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Enough for that run, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在往外运吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ferry it out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-父亲 -伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Father. -Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能聊聊吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May we speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有选我进远征军 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why wasn't I chosen for the expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我以为你要去西部 -不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Thought you were going west. -Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先做点 配得上努门诺尔人做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not till I've done something worthy of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么事呢 用你自己的话来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what is that? In your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我描述不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have words for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才非常努力地寻找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why I'm trying so hard to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来寻求您的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why I'm asking for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是希望能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wish I could provide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但志愿者的数量 远远超出了我们能容纳的范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we've far more volunteers than we could ever hope to accommodate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这城市有一半的人想要登上那些船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half the city wants a spot on those boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我塞进队列的前排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slip me to the front of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are your qualifications?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-“资格”  -你隶属于海上卫队吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-"Qualifications"? -Do you belong to the Sea Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你明知道我比水手厉害得多… -你隶属于海上卫队吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know I'm twice the sailor... -Do you belong to the Sea Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王卫队呢 商人公会呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the Queen's Guard? Merchant's Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看来有正式编制才是重点 -骑士公会呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-This is about uniform. -Horseman's Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太扯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're being absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在假装 忠于这座岛上的传统的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}While you were feigning fidelity to the traditions of this isle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人已经在将传统发扬光大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}these men were living them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想尽办法贡献力量 志愿出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finding ways to contribute. To serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西显然你并不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something of which you evidently care little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎 而且我准备好出征了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care. I'm ready to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这件事能让我感到自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing would make me prouder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你错失了良机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you had your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你已经做出了选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you made your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让努门诺尔人冒着生命之险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Risk Númenorean lives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了一些肮脏的中洲南方人 和一个好战的精灵 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for some grimy Southlander and a warmongering Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉宗国师  你为什么要让我们的亲人去送死 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consul Pharaz?n! Why are you sending our kinsmen off to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉宗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-法拉宗  -跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Pharaz?n! -Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我没发消息 这周太难熬了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me for not sending word to you sooner. Been a trying week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么不阻止这一切 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't he stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他忠于女王 不论对… -肯定是错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's loyal to her. Rightly or... -Wrongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人和你感觉一样 但这还不足以改变他的想法 但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are many who feel as you do. Not enough to sway him yet, but 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你可以去说服他 他会听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}given the right push... Then it must be you. He will listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开口说话 他就闭耳塞听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I speak, his ears close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就大点声说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So speak louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中洲南方人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi, Southlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人接下来去哪里了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And where did the enemy head next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为敌人继续往南 朝着欧斯提力斯瞭望塔进军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Further south, I should think. Towards the watchtower of Ostirith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去通知海上卫队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll inform the Sea Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 哈尔布兰德大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My thanks, Lord Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢肯定 等我们登陆后 你的民众一定会发挥重要作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm certain your fellowship will prove just as invaluable once we make landfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登陆 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Landfall?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔告知我们 你希望团结你的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel informed us of your aspiration to unite your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然这样说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她绝非未加思考脱口而出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I trust she was not speaking in haste?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我的本意是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a matter of fact, it was my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴只是觉得肩上的任务很重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My companion is merely feeling the weight of his task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我毫不怀疑 到时候 他会尽自己的一份力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no doubt, come time, he will do his part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经为本次任务背书 希望他能如你所说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Given that I've staked my name upon it, I should hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄政女王 您父亲请您去一趟塔里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen Regent, your father has requested your presence in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“加拉德瑞尔告知我们”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Galadriel informed us."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得当时 女王居然知道要去她父亲床边堵截我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wondered how the queen knew to waylay me at her father's bedside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没曾想到你为了公会徽章背叛了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It never occurred to me you'd hand me over for a guild crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前恳求你放过我 但你却利用了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You used me. After I all but begged you to let me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚说服努门诺尔派出五艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have just convinced Númenor to send five ships
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和五百人来帮助你的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and 500 men to aid your people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你加冕为王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and place a crown upon your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人可能会认为是你利用了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many might assume you used me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦另找别人去加冕吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find another head to crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 迪莉 只是树而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's okay, Dil. It's just the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们选这条路是失心疯了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What madness made them go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头足路就应该被封起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rockfoot Pass must be blocked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑路难行 继续前进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Won't get any easier in the dark. Keep movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“天黑路难行”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Easier in the dark."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不告诉我到底发生了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you tell me what's really goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年的这个时节 这些树林从没有这样光秃秃过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These woods have never been this bare this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因太显而易见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's as plain as lip fungus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪他 不是吗 那个大家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is responsible, isn't he? The big fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我怎么做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What precisely do you expect me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你当初在营地就该做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you ought to have done at the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卸掉他们的推车轮子 丢下他们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Take their wheels and leave them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎么样你才肯做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's it gonna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得有人变成寡妇 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make a widow of somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者孤儿吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or an orphan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People are gettin' hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟紧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很奇怪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, this is very strange. Most peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常奇怪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你们差点吓死我了 -玛尔娃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You nearly caused my heart to burst. -Malva.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们看到脚印了 -在泥里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We saw footprints. -In the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们一个一个说 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lots of 'em! -One at a time, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快跑 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori! Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 快躲开 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori, get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nori! Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 它会咬到你的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! It'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚守阵地 安塔摩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold your ground, Ontamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你的父亲感到骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make your father proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的击打动作 像北荒原的岩石巨人一样笨拙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their strokes fall like the Stone-giants of the North Moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有对付这个敌人的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are untested against this foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许精灵愿意提供一些指导 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps the Elf would be willing to offer some instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死奥克的方法有很多种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are many ways to kill an Orc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对你们而言 我建议用简洁有力的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for you, I will keep it strong and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛刺 旋扭 拔出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stab, twist, gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我比划一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看谁能伤得了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will see who can score flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁能打赢精灵 我会提拔他为…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone that does, I will promote...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑法的核心是平衡 而并非力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swordsmanship is about balance, rather than strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战要用你的双脚 而不是双臂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fight with your feet. Not your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个精灵正在广场上与一名士兵切磋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Elf is fighting a soldier in the square.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚不要站定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't plant roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不断移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠蛮力永远无法战胜奥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never trust brute force to best an Orc.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以谋略制胜往往是最容易的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's often easiest to outmaneuver them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来都不知道 铁匠的助手能有这般功夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never known a smith's aide who could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在叫停这一切还为时不晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not too late to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.75,0:25:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然权杖在你堂姐手中 但众人追随的领袖是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your cousin may hold the scepter, but it's you the people follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在众人的帮助下 你可以… -可以什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-With their help you could... -Could what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.58,0:25:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施加你的影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assert your influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的时候 年轻人的愚蠢足以把年长者气哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes the folly of youth is enough to make an old man weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.95,0:25:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图阻止战争算愚蠢吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it folly to try and stop a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.33,0:25:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆流而上是愚蠢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's folly to kick against the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 潮水可能涨起来淹死人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, the tide may rise and drown a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能落潮把人卷入海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or fall and sweep him out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.91,0:25:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制潮水的诀窍 是要知道它接下来会朝哪个方向流动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trick of mastering the current is to know which way it will turn next.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.95,0:25:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾单枪匹马阻止了上一任国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all but single-handedly prevented our last king
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.41,0:25:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们拖回老路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from dragging us back to the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别告诉我你现在无法 改变弥瑞尔的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tell me you couldn't sway Míriel's mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.91,0:25:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么让你觉得 弥瑞尔和我的想法不一致 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what makes you think Míriel's mind and my own are not as one on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.66,0:25:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我父亲宁可死 也不会接受精灵的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because my father would sooner die than take orders from an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.08,0:26:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“精灵的命令” \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Orders from an Elf"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.87,0:26:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等这一切结束之后 将会是精灵们听从我们的号令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When all this has ended, Elves will take orders from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.62,0:26:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我堂姐愿意 她可以为加拉德瑞尔出战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, my cousin can go to war for Galadriel if she wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.37,0:26:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是为了努门诺尔而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I go to war for Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.29,0:26:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么会是为努门诺尔而战呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could this be for Númenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.33,0:26:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都白学了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you learned nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.50,0:26:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 我们将拯救中洲的下等人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, we will save the low men of Middle-earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.37,0:26:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬高他们的地位 给他们期待已久的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}lift them up, and give them the king they've long awaited.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.87,0:26:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国王将永远欠我们的债\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A king who will be forever in our debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.25,0:26:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你现在能不能想明白 这会对我们有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, contemplate, if you can, how that might benefit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.04,0:26:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矿石 森林 贸易 贡品…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ores, forests, trades, tribute...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.00,0:26:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我可不敢 阻止这场战争 给我千金都不换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't dare stop that. Not for all the salt in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:27:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不应该阻止这场战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And neither should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.87,0:27:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座王国 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.29,0:27:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这座王国处于危险之中 我必须… -危险已经过去了 父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The kingdom is in danger. I must... -The danger has passed, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.12,0:27:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在做 您一直认为我们必须做的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are doing now what you always believed we must.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.70,0:27:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在恢复与精灵的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're restoring our connection with the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.29,0:27:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥瑞尔 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Míriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.08,0:27:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在呢 父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.91,0:27:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.04,0:27:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't go to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 等待你的将是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All that awaits you there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.83,0:28:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 父亲 等待我的将是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, Father? What awaits me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.20,0:28:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.54,0:28:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢信吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.25,0:28:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在说你刚才做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's talkin' about what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.12,0:28:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有见过他们 这样满心喜欢一个外族人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never seen 'em take a shine to an outsider like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.37,0:28:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带了一些蜂蜡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brought you some beeswax.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.33,0:28:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你那大爪子上涂一点就没那么疼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slather some on that paw, should help with the tenderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.00,0:29:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.08,0:30:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬我们两个伟大种族之间的长久联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To an enduring union between our two great peoples,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.54,0:30:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡扎德人和诺多族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khazad and Noldor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.54,0:30:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-敬联盟 -敬联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-To the union. -To the union.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.29,0:30:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们开怀畅饮之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before our wines ascend,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.16,0:30:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林大人 我想赞扬你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord Durin, I should like to commend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.70,0:30:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡扎督姆一向被称为 矮人王国中最安静的一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khazad-d?m has been called the quietest of Dwarven kingdoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.91,0:30:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近几个月 据说你们的熔炉在燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but in recent months, your furnaces are said to be burning
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.12,0:30:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火光亮得都快赶上奥力本尊的眼睛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as bright as the eyes of Aul? himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.66,0:30:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你们的矿井钻得越来越深\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mines delving ever deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.58,0:30:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股新的活力您认为出自哪里呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To what do you credit this new invigoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.62,0:30:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的话我也想问林顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might ask the same of Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.20,0:30:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用船送走精灵战士 扩建城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shipping off its warriors, expandin' its cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.41,0:31:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对精灵来说有点突然 不是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bit sudden for Elves, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.58,0:31:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们每做一个决定 通常都要花他个好几年…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Typically takes you people weeks just to decide to take a sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.41,0:31:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.25,0:31:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我们精灵而言 时间流逝得很慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hand of time crawls so slowly for our kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.16,0:31:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们经常会把 多年的辛苦努力视为短暂的付出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We often overlook the years of effort we perceive as taking but a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.33,0:31:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们这样不会冒犯到我们的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In so doing, I would not wish to offend our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.25,0:31:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能被一个真诚的提问所冒犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would think our Dwarven friend far too stout of heart
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.58,0:31:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这位矮人朋友未免也太顽固了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be offended by an honest inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.83,0:31:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个真诚的问题想问你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have an honest inquiry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.16,0:31:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里弄来的这张桌子 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From where did you procure the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.50,0:31:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么问 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.00,0:31:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种石头只分布在一定的深度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This stone grows only at certain depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别稀少 以至于 我们的共鸣者很少能找到矿床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So rarely do our resonators locate a deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.83,0:31:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将每一块这种石头 都视为珍贵的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We consider each to be a precious gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.58,0:31:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它留着用于最神圣的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We reserve its use for the most sacred purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.29,0:32:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来建造纪念碑或坟墓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monuments or tombs,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.54,0:32:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪念我们尊敬的逝者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to our honored dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.08,0:32:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我们的亵渎 都林大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please forgive our sacrilege, Lord Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.04,0:32:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会让你 把它带回家 好让它得到应有的尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shall have to send it home with you, so it can be treated with proper respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.83,0:32:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴知道 精灵当中还是存在些许荣誉感的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to know there's still some honor left among the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.16,0:32:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.70,0:32:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 敬我们两族人民的联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the union of our two peoples, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.25,0:32:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the union.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.95,0:32:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这个矮人的忠诚令人钦佩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your loyalty to the Dwarf is admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.41,0:32:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应这样忠诚待友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loyalty to a friend ought to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.25,0:32:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论种族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regardless of his race.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.04,0:33:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这个 你就可以向国王撒谎吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does it justify lying to your king?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.33,0:33:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 我想知道 一直在对我撒谎的是不是您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder, High King, if it is in fact you who has been lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.75,0:33:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着友谊的提议 去了卡扎督姆 但事实上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went to Khazad-d?m with a proposal of friendship, but in truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.66,0:33:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却在寻求 更看得见摸得着的东西 不是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you sought something far more tangible, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.75,0:33:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你熟悉 《希斯艾格利尔山根之歌》吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you familiar with The Song of the Roots of Hithaeglir?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.75,0:33:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请复述给我听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Recount it for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.50,0:33:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个鲜为人知的传说 大多数人认为它是杜撰的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An obscure legend regarded by most to be a apocryphal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.91,0:33:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复述一遍 埃尔隆德佩瑞蒂尔（“半精灵”）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Recount it, Elrond Peredhel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.95,0:33:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌讲述了一场战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It speaks of a battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.83,0:33:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迷雾山脉高耸的山峰之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}high among the peaks of the Misty Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.29,0:33:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗并非因荣耀 或使命而起 而是因为一棵树\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not over honor or duty. But over a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.83,0:33:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人称这棵树里 藏着最后一颗丢失的精灵宝钻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Within which some claim was hidden the last of the lost Silmarils.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.58,0:34:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的一方是一位精灵战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On one side, fought an Elven warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.29,0:34:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心如曼威般纯洁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a heart as pure as Manw?,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护这棵树 他将所有的光都倾注其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who poured all of his light into the tree to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.79,0:34:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的另一方是魔苟斯的一个炎魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-On the other, a Balrog of Morgoth,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.41,0:34:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他所有的仇恨 都传导到这棵树上 以求将其摧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who channeled all his hatred into the tree to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.58,0:34:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们无休止的决斗中 闪电击中了这棵树…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amidst their duel unending, lightning ensnared the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.12,0:34:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使他们的对抗造就了一股力量…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forging of their conflict, a power...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.70,0:34:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股力量如善良一般纯净而轻盈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A power as pure and light as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.95,0:34:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又像邪恶一样坚强不屈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As strong and unyielding as evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.95,0:34:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这股力量从树根渗入大山深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say it seeped down the roots into the mountain depths,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.04,0:34:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个世纪以来 它一直在等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where for centuries now, it has waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.41,0:34:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是承认矮人确实找到了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you admit the Dwarves did find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.08,0:34:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种矿石蕴含着丢失的精灵宝钻之光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ore containing the light of the lost Silmaril.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.25,0:34:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只承认这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I admit only this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.16,0:34:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应过都林永远不会 泄露他子民的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promised Durin never to reveal his people's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.04,0:35:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说 信守对他子民的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what if keeping your promise to his people
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.66,0:35:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着你的同胞就要厄运难逃呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}meant ensuring the doom of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.58,0:35:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们第一次注意到这种情况 刚好在加拉德瑞尔回来之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We first took notice of it just prior to Galadriel's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.95,0:35:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我们希望通过把她送走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We hoped that by sending her away,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.83,0:35:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹去战争最后的痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and so bringing an end to the last vestiges of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.62,0:35:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而就此阻止树的枯萎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we might arrest the decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.91,0:35:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但尽管我们竭尽全力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But despite our every effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.83,0:35:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯萎还是加速了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our decline has only quickened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.75,0:36:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这棵树表面上的枯萎反映了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The blight upon this tree is but an outer manifestation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内在的实质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of an inner reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.41,0:36:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵族之光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That the light of the Eldar,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.66,0:36:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我们的光 正在消逝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our light, is fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁知道这件事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.04,0:36:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有极少数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Precious few.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.62,0:36:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再问最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ask again, and for the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.50,0:36:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人是不是找到了那种矿石 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}did the Dwarves find the ore or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.33,0:36:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向都林发过誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swore an oath to Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.16,0:36:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对有些人来说 如今发誓可能并没有多大意义了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To some, that may now hold little weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.54,0:36:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我看来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in my esteem,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.00,0:36:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是誓言才让 我们的灵魂紧紧连接在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it is by such things our very souls are bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.50,0:36:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算仅仅为了希望而违背誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not intend to let mine slip away on the basis of mere hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.33,0:37:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望从来都不是微不足道的 埃尔隆德…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hope is never mere, Elrond...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.66,0:37:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便希望很渺茫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even when it is meager.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.66,0:37:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当所有其他感官都睡着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When all other senses sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.12,0:37:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望之眼会率先醒来 最后一个闭上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the eye of hope is first to awaken, last to shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.54,0:37:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果精灵现在放弃中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Elves abandon Middle-earth now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.79,0:37:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗大军将会在中洲大地上横行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the armies of darkness will march over the face of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.54,0:37:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将会是末日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.87,0:37:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是我们精灵族的末日 还是所有种族的末日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not just of our people, but all peoples.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.58,0:37:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能防止这种情况发生的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the hope of preventing that is not reason enough
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.66,0:37:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不足以让你重新考虑你的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make you reconsider your oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.12,0:37:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不妨再找一条出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suggest you find another.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.41,0:38:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由诸神之手创造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was the land immortal hands
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.75,0:38:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从隔离之海中升起的那地是何地 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rose up from Sundering Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.08,0:38:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩赐之地 星引之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Land of the gift, land of the star
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.50,0:38:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将永远闪耀 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To shine eternally?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.00,0:38:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是努门诺尔 美丽的努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Twas Númenor Fair Númenor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.54,0:38:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明亮之岛充满了恩惠优雅…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bright isle filled with grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.25,0:38:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说不会有危险的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said it won't be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.16,0:38:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打赌等我下船的时候 一切就都结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wager it'll all be over by the time I get off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.12,0:38:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要告诉我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just don't tell my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.58,0:38:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逢人便夸 未来的女婿是个战争英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He keeps crowing to everyone with ears, his future son-in-law's a war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.16,0:38:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱吧 来吧 唱起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sing! Come on, sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.25,0:38:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得歌词吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember the words, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.04,0:38:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你鬼哭狼嚎了一宿 恐怕歌词我永远都忘不掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After hearing you squawk them all night, I fear I'll never forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.08,0:38:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许伊熙尔杜会和你一起唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps Isildur will sing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.16,0:38:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就有意思了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.87,0:39:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们伟大的岛屿永远屹立 让我们的剑战胜死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make our great land to ever stand Our swords to conquer death
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.20,0:39:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-答案是不行 -我还什么都没说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The answer's no. -I haven't said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.16,0:39:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你15年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've known you 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.45,0:39:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真觉得 我不知道你来是要说什么吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I don't know what you're here to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.91,0:39:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-其实是16年 但我的意思是… -安塔摩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It's actually 16, but I mean... -Ontamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.29,0:39:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我来是要说什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. What have I come to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.83,0:39:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要非常诚恳地道歉 当然了 安塔摩肯定会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fairly lavish apology, which Ontamo, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立马接受道歉 但我可不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would've accepted instantly, but I wouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.08,0:39:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.50,0:39:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意道歉 只是因为你觉得现在我升职了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're only apologizing because you think now that I've been promoted,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.66,0:39:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以带你参加远征军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can get you on the expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.95,0:39:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可以带我吗  -我就说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Can you? -Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.12,0:39:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想说 我不会马上接受你的道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd just like to say, I wouldn't have accepted instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.25,0:39:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我很高兴你道歉了 -他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-But I am glad that you apologized. -No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.25,0:39:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.62,0:39:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很乐意再道一次 对不起 是我挑起了那次争执\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'll gladly do it again. I'm sorry I started the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.70,0:39:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在请带上我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now please bring me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.62,0:39:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底要怎么做才能弥补过错 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'll it take to make this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.37,0:39:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你可以随便打我一拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine, you get a free hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.66,0:40:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下巴或肚子都可以 任打一拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jaw, gut, your choice. One hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.25,0:40:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.87,0:40:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.91,0:40:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉被打了三拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That felt like three.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.91,0:40:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那你们能带我上船吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you'll bring me on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.20,0:40:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔杜 你是我相处最久的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur, you're my oldest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.95,0:40:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 现在你可能 仍然是我最好的朋友 但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you want to know the truth, you're probably still my best, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.08,0:40:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么了  -安塔摩 拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What? -Ontamo, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.66,0:40:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 凭良心 我不能为你背书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't, in good conscience, stake my name
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.16,0:40:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐你履行一项你可能会放弃的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}recommending you for a duty that you might well decide to abandon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.25,0:40:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次会不一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It'll be different this time. -Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.20,0:40:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望有一天会不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One day, I hope it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.62,0:40:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望有一天你能找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One day, I hope you find something
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.41,0:40:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意为之牺牲一切的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you would be willing to sacrifice anything for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.83,0:40:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你照顾贝雷克的 我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take care of Berek for you. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.75,0:41:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝雷克要去 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berek's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.00,0:41:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯马师把他招来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The horsemaster recruited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.33,0:41:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 伊熙尔杜 大海永远是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Isil. The sea is always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.16,0:42:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要偷渡出去吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you stowing away?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.25,0:42:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要把这艘船烧掉吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you about to burn the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.95,0:42:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上离开这里 我不会告诉任何人我看到过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of here this moment. I won't let anyone know I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.75,0:42:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把灯递给我 -别过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hand me the lantern. -Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.50,0:42:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把灯给我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.41,0:42:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家召集起来 快点 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gather every hand. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.50,0:42:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们救上来 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get them out. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.62,0:42:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们救上来  伊熙尔杜 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get them out! Isildur?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.33,0:43:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔杜 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.62,0:43:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.41,0:43:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才在一艘渔船上 一定是有酒桶爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was in a fishing boat. A cask must've gone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.66,0:43:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒桶 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A cask?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.91,0:43:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.00,0:43:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本可以丢下我 但他却救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could've just left, but he saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.66,0:43:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有理由怀疑 是一个经过的强盗所为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have reason to suspect a passing brigand,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.41,0:43:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但暂时还没有确认其身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we've yet to identify him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.41,0:43:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很走运 其他的船只没有被烧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're fortunate we didn't lose the rest of the ships as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.08,0:43:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这显然是意图激起你的疑虑 摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was clearly an attempt to kindle your doubts, Queen Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.91,0:43:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别上当 -我不敢苟同精灵的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do not let it. -I'm forced to disagree with the Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.29,0:44:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们确实操之过急了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we did act in haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.79,0:44:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王国应该被带领 而不是被拖拽着走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A kingdom should be led. Not dragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.33,0:44:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我建议推迟出航\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I recommend we delay the voyage
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.20,0:44:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先为您的事业赢得更多的民心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we've had time enough to win more hearts to your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.00,0:44:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人一天比一天强大 也许每犹豫一小时 敌人就更强大些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy grows stronger every day. Perhaps every hour we hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.08,0:44:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要记住你为什么 选择了这条路 记住你的信念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember why you chose this path. Remember your faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.45,0:44:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我能忘记吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think I could forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有三艘船 而且还有你父亲的祝福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We still have three ships. And your father's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.37,0:44:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔布兰德大人呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What of Lord Halbrand?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.79,0:44:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在等待我们启航\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He awaits our departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.37,0:44:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.37,0:44:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要不要让海上卫队先撤下来 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall I tell the Sea Guard to stand down?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.41,0:44:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天一亮就重新召开会议 做最后的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This council will reconvene at first light to make a final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.50,0:44:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确保哈尔布兰德大人参会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See to it Lord Halbrand attends.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.66,0:45:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能确定的是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you been able to ascertain?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.58,0:45:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德 原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.62,0:45:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅你 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.95,0:45:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我没有早点告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I did not tell you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.25,0:45:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你早就知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.25,0:45:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始 我就求至高王把我们的秘密告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I begged him to allow you into our confidence from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.91,0:45:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不同意这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the High King forbade it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.70,0:45:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘银…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this... this mithril...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.29,0:45:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们唯一的救赎吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is our only salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.08,0:45:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德 我在各种恶劣条件下都测试过它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond, I have tested it under every duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.29,0:45:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事物都无法削弱它的光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing diminishes its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.95,0:45:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信 如果能快速获得大量秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We believe if we can secure vast quantities of it quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.54,0:45:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多到足以再次 让每一个精灵浸润在维拉之光中…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}enough to saturate every last Elf in the light of the Valar once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.62,0:45:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.50,0:45:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 它是我们唯一的救赎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. It very well could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.16,0:46:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.50,0:46:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王骗了我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That the High King deceived me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.25,0:46:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 我们精灵 注定要灭亡 除非我违背誓言 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or that now our people are doomed unless I break an oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.54,0:46:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛朋友 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And betray a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.83,0:46:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德 你父亲启航的那个晚上我在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was there, Elrond, the night your father set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.45,0:46:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一介凡人 相信自己可以说服众神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A mortal man, who believed he could convince the very Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.04,0:46:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们参战帮助我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to come to war in our aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.91,0:46:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到你妈妈恳求他不要去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard your mother pleading with him not to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.29,0:46:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求他 哀求他别去 问他为什么非他不可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}asking him, imploring him, why, why must it be him?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.37,0:46:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你父亲说了什么吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you know what he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.54,0:47:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说因为他是 唯一一个能做这件事的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he was the only one who could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.54,0:47:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了 不应该利用你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wrong to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.87,0:47:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For that, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.58,0:47:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 女王会传唤你觐见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow, the queen will call you to audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.62,0:47:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在会面上的态度 很可能会决定这次任务的成败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your voice at that meeting may well decide whether this mission stands or falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.04,0:47:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-帮帮我 -我想我已经帮你够多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Help me. -I think I've helped you quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.50,0:47:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就帮帮你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.83,0:47:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再和我内斗了 跟我一起与敌人战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop fighting me, and together, let us fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.41,0:47:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前 我这类人却还在与敌人为伍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not so long ago, men like me were fighting alongside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.83,0:47:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是你的同胞 并不包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Men like you. Not you, yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.00,0:48:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.33,0:48:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道 我在坐上那艘木筏之前做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know what I did before I ended up on that raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.58,0:48:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我是怎么活下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know how I survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.37,0:48:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所有人是如何得以幸存的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How we all survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.62,0:48:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被这些人发现 他们会把我赶出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when these people discover it, they will cast me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.45,0:48:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.04,0:48:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候要找到光 我们必须先触及黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes to find the light, we must first touch the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.45,0:48:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对黑暗了解多少 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you know of darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.25,0:49:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 那把短剑是谁的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose dagger was it, Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.08,0:49:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失去的是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is it you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.83,0:49:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.50,0:49:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出什么事了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.83,0:49:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被杀害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.54,0:49:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个充斥着黑暗和绝望的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a place of darkness and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.87,0:49:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被索隆的仆从所杀 这样你满意了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By servants of Sauron. Is that enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.66,0:49:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是为了复仇 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So this is about vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.25,0:49:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区复仇远远无法让我满足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One cannot satisfy thirst by drinking seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.70,0:49:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是为了什么  你为什么要一直战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what is it? Why do you keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.16,0:49:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在要我去一个 我发誓永远不会回去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are asking me to go to the one place that I swore never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.33,0:49:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以起码你可以告诉我为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The least you can do is tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.37,0:49:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要一直战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.25,0:49:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我停不下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I cannot stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.08,0:49:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我领导的军队对我倒戈相向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The company I led mutinied against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.75,0:49:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最亲密的朋友 与至高王密谋将我流放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My closest friend conspired with the king to exile me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.50,0:50:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他们每个人之所以这样做…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And each of them acted as they did...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.91,0:50:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他们再也无法将我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I believe they could no longer distinguish me...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.20,0:50:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我正在抗争的邪恶区分开来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the evil I was fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.16,0:50:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.91,0:50:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.45,0:50:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及所有这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.75,0:50:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你感到难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.33,0:50:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的悲伤无法减轻我的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your sorrow cannot ease my pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈尊当个铁匠也不会减轻你的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nor will a hammer and tongs ease yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.62,0:50:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里不会找到内心的平静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no peace to be found for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.50,0:50:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nor for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.12,0:50:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持久的平静在这里无处可寻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No lasting peace in any path,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.58,0:50:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在隔离之海的对岸觅得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that which lies across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.58,0:50:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经战斗了几个世纪 试图得到我内心的平静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have fought for centuries, seeking to earn mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.37,0:50:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得这样做才能获得平静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is how you earn yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.33,0:51:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天我已经等待很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long have I awaited this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.66,0:51:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待您的同类终将归来的这天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The day your kind would return at last,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.45,0:51:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们从淤泥和污秽中拯救出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}lift us up from the muck and the filth,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.04,0:51:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在您身边找回自己的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to take our rightful place at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.04,0:51:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向您保证我对您的忠诚至死不渝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I pledge my undying service to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.62,0:51:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向索隆宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I pledge my loyalty to Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.95,0:52:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是索隆吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are Sauron, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.79,0:52:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…等等…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.04,0:52:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那无论您是谁 我都效忠于您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll serve you, then. Whoever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.62,0:52:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有双手沾血才能证明忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only blood can bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.70,0:52:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃德雷格 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waldreg?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.33,0:52:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃德雷格…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waldreg...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.20,0:53:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃德雷格 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waldreg, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.12,0:53:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.79,0:53:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.08,0:53:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.08,0:53:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.70,0:53:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次瞄高一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lift your aim next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.37,0:53:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么害怕弓弦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And don't be so afraid of the string.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.25,0:53:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何苦要费心教我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why bother trying to teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.95,0:53:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我花了两百多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it took me over 200 years
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.75,0:53:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有了今晚站在这里的勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to develop the bravery that's keeping me standing here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.79,0:53:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你仅仅14岁就有这样的勇气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You found it in only 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.79,0:53:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中我们需要这种勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're going to need it in the fight to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.66,0:53:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我一生中 你们精灵一直监视着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All my life, your kind has watched us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.12,0:53:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清点我们说过的每一句悄悄话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Counting every whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.66,0:53:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留意每一把过于锋利的餐刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every kitchen knife too sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.16,0:53:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都快要被埋在这座瞭望塔里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all about to be buried in this tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.75,0:53:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何苦还要跟我们一起陪葬呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So why be buried with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.41,0:54:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在清点悄悄话和餐刀的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because in counting the whispers and the knives,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.33,0:54:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始了解在它们背后的活生生的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've come to know the voices and the hands of those behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.25,0:54:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人已经走了一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half of us just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.83,0:54:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还有一半选择了留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But half stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.12,0:54:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.83,0:54:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 瞄高一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So lift your aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.08,0:54:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事你不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.41,0:54:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前见过这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.04,0:55:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一把钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.37,0:55:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人用一些失传的手艺所制 用来奴役你的祖先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Conjured by some forgotten craft of the enemy, to enslave your ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.95,0:55:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么的钥匙 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A key to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.87,0:55:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.37,0:55:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方指挥官说过要成为神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The enemy commander spoke of becoming a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.25,0:55:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这些土地上给奥克一个家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of giving the Orcs a home in these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.91,0:56:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管他有什么阴谋 有一点是肯定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But whatever his design, this much is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.08,0:56:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人知道你儿子 有他需要用来启动计划的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy knows your son has what he needs to enact it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.45,0:56:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.20,0:56:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.04,0:56:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.41,0:56:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会活下来的 布隆温\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can survive this, Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.79,0:56:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.79,0:56:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.66,0:56:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.33,0:56:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 向敌人低头 意味着你就夺走了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Bow to the enemy, and you take away everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.62,0:56:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走了子孙后代的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From your son, and his sons after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.33,0:56:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们祖辈辛勤劳作了 整整一个纪元 才赢回了自己的品性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your people have worked an entire age to earn back their virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.04,0:56:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅因为一时的绝望 你就要让它前功尽弃吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you undo it all in just one moment of despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.08,0:57:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定还有别的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There must be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.16,0:57:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那说出来听听 我求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Name it. I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.16,0:57:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说错吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.70,0:57:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们盯着我们是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were right to watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.04,0:57:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们注定要堕入黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because we are destined for the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.20,0:57:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的生存方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's how we survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.83,0:57:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们就是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps it's who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.33,0:57:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远将会是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who we will always be.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.75,0:57:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于风险之中的 可远远不只有我们的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's far more at stake here than just our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.75,0:57:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年魔苟斯开战 整个贝烈瑞安德都沦陷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When Morgoth was at war, whole continents sank.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.75,0:57:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁能说得出 这次会引发什么样的可怕后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is to say what horrors this might unleash,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.50,0:57:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该让敌人得逞吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should our enemy obtain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.25,0:57:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有什么力量去阻止他 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What power do we have to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.87,0:57:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看周围 已经完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look around. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.87,0:57:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-还没有 -很快就要完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Not yet. -Soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.41,0:57:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等敌人向我们进军时 这座瞭望塔就会倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when they march upon us, this tower will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.87,0:58:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.25,0:58:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.33,0:58:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.29,0:58:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.45,0:58:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.00,0:58:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.91,0:59:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你是瞎编的 不是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You made it up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.08,0:59:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莎多年来 一直想要一张新桌子 所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disa's been wanting a new table for years, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.37,0:59:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快得了 这桌子哪有那么重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, come on, it's not that heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.20,0:59:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到负担沉重的 不是这张桌子的重量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is not the weight of the table that burdens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.04,0:59:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不说出来 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So why don't you come out with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.75,0:59:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为负担拿出来分担 有可能会减半 也有可能会加倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because a burden shared may either be halved or doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.70,0:59:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取决于听话人的同理心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Depending on the heart that receives it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.95,0:59:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥力的胡子啊 你别绕弯子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aul?'s beard! Enough with the quail sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.83,0:59:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大方方说 不用避讳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me the meat, and give it to me raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.58,0:59:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有对你说实话 都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have not been truthful with you, Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.95,0:59:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来卡扎督姆 并非为了友谊 而是有目的而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not come to Khazad-d?m for friendship, but ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.33,0:59:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我之前并不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.29,0:59:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此行的任务是寻找秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I came for mithril.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.04,0:59:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.00,1:00:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without it,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.50,1:00:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们精灵族要么 得在春天离开这些海岸 要么灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my kind must either abandon these shores by spring, or perish.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.79,1:00:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭亡 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perish?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.50,1:00:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么灭亡 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perish how?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.16,1:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不朽的灵魂将化为乌有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our immortal souls will dwindle into nothing,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.54,1:00:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢衰减耗尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}slowly diminishing,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.16,1:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我们变成虚影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we are but shadows,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.20,1:00:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被时间的潮汐冲走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}swept away by the tides of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.75,1:00:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不复生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.95,1:00:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以整个精灵族的命运 都掌握在我手中 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the fate of the entire Elven race is in my hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.70,1:00:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it would appear.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.62,1:01:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.50,1:01:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个精灵族的命运都掌握在你手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fate of the entire Elven race is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.04,1:01:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的手中 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.75,1:01:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.41,1:01:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起你那软弱的玻璃心 我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fetch your feathery shirts. Let's start walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.62,1:01:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都林… -先别急着谢我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Durin... -Don't thank me yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.08,1:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们想办法 说服我父亲之后 再谢我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank me after we find a way to convince my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.91,1:01:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们可以动身了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now can we please get moving?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.20,1:01:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的路很长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a long journey back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.12,1:01:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些阳光都开始让我胃不舒服了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And all this sunlight is startin' to give me a sour stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.70,1:02:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个条件 你告诉迪莎这张桌子是我给的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Under one condition. Tell Disa the table's from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.37,1:02:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别得寸进尺 精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't push your luck, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.83,1:02:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔布兰德大人 摄政女王召见您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord Halbrand, the Queen Regent summons you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.25,1:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看是谁又靠他爹弄到了一个位置啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look whose father secured him a post. Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.33,1:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自己争取到的 和你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I earned mine. Same as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.29,1:04:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.75,1:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向驯马师报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Report to the horsemaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.70,1:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我是骑兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought I was in cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.29,1:04:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的确是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.95,1:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责清扫马厩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.79,1:05:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.70,1:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳索 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear the lines!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.66,1:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扬帆远航 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Square the sail!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.58,1:06:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们朝东北方向行进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We head nor'-east.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.95,1:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.79,1:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.45,1:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳正在落下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sun is fast falling
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.83,1:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落在森岩的树林后方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beneath trees of stone
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.29,1:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔中之光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The light in the tower
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.33,1:07:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No longer my home
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.45,1:07:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去灯火朦胧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Past eyes of pale fire
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.25,1:07:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沙做我的睡床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Black sand for my bed
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.58,1:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用所知的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I trade all I've known
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.00,1:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换取未知的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the unknown ahead
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.79,1:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤我 遥远之地 请呼唤我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call to me Call to me lands far away
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.12,1:07:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我现在 必须在这流浪的日子里游荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For I must now wander this wandering day
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.91,1:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须游荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Away I must wander
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.58,1:07:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这流浪的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wandering day
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.25,1:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我缺水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of drink I have little
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.83,1:08:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我少食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And food I have less
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.95,1:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量告诉我不行 但是这条路要求我踏足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My strength tells me no But the path demands yes
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.41,1:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我双腿很短 而道阻且长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My legs are so short And the way is so long
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.45,1:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法休息 何谈舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've no rest nor comfort
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.45,1:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所慰藉 唯有歌声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No comfort, but song
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.33,1:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我歌唱 遥远之地 请为我歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sing to me, sing to me Lands far away
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.79,1:08:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请起身指引我度过这流浪的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, rise up and guide me This wandering day
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.33,1:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请答应要找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please promise to find me
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.29,1:08:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这流浪的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wandering day
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.12,1:08:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 他们的答案来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At last comes their answer
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.00,1:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过寒冷和霜冻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Through cold and through frost
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.04,1:08:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有的流浪者都身陷迷途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That not all who wonder or wander are lost
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.83,1:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter the sorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.70,1:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不计成本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter the cost
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.79,1:09:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有的流浪者都身陷迷途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That not all who wonder Or wander are... Lost
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.37,1:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译：腐哥
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.45,1:09:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创意监督 罗婷婷

